# =============================================================================
# File: /opt/ansible-k3s-cluster/README.cluster-upgrade-path
# =============================================================================
# Purpose:
#   Document the recommended upgrade path for:
#     - Kernel versions
#     - distcc versions
#     - Raspberry Pi firmware
#     - k3s versions
#
# Upgrade Path:
#
#   1. Kernel Upgrade
#      - Build new kernel on builder
#      - Verify artifacts
#      - Deploy via deploy-kernel.yml
#      - Run verification pipeline
#
#   2. distcc Upgrade
#      - Upgrade builder first
#      - Upgrade worker nodes
#      - Run distcc-test.yml
#
#   3. Firmware Upgrade
#      - Update EEPROM
#      - Update /boot firmware files
#      - Reboot nodes sequentially
#
#   4. k3s Upgrade
#      - Upgrade controller first
#      - Upgrade workers
#      - Validate workloads
#
# Notes:
#   - This file defines the authoritative upgrade sequence.
# =============================================================================
